	Local $sFile = FileOpenDialog("Select a playlist...", @UserProfileDir & "\Music", $ImportPlaylistFormatFilter, $FD_FILEMUSTEXIST, "", $GUI_Main_Handle) ;Later I'll implement multiple playlists

